OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'I clung to the boat as it 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsank' - DR Congo survivor  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some of the 189 people rescued after a 
OL,6, boat capsized in the Democratic        
OL,7, Republic of Congo have told the BBC how
OL,8, they managed to survive.               
OL,10,F"All my body was under the water,      
OL,11,Fexcept my head. I clung to a wooden    
OL,12,Fpart of the boat until some people     
OL,13,Farrived with a canoe to save me," said 
OL,14,FKorami Mopole.                         
OL,16,FMore than 40 bodies have been recovered
OL,17,Fso far, while rescue workers are       
OL,18,Fsearching for 167 people still missing.
OL,20,FThe boat was reportedly overloaded.    
